This paper deals with the analysis of time delays in the publication of CVEs and their associated CVSS scores. It involves the study of software vulnerabilities and their impact on security. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other possible sub-categories include cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
